  "text": "Previous research has also looked at aggregating information from multiple sources to answer specific questions. [CITATION_1] studied how to collect information from multiple sources over the Web, specifically to find answers using corroborative evidence from multiple sources. [CITATION_2] looked at how to collect information from contrasting viewpoints. The work presented in this paper looks at the next step of how to present these documents with contrasting viewpoints to users, while also providing information about credibility of the sources, to enable users to learn about the topic efficiently.",
